'''Knowt's Disease''' was a degenerative affliction that destroyed body tissue. [[Pter Thanas]] died of it less than five [[Standard year/Legends|years]] after being diagnosed.<ref name="AS">''[[Assault at Selonia]]''</ref> The wealthy [[Coruscanti/Legends|Coruscanti]] businessman, [[Archa Sabis]] was afflicted with a non-lethal form of the disease. His right arm and part of his face and torso were affected by the disease and replaced by [[Cybernetics/Legends|cybernetic]] prostheses.<ref name="CatCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

